# 🧑‍💼 User Stories – Customfolio

## User Accounts

1. **As a new user**, I want to sign up with my email or Google account, so that I can securely access and save my job application data.  
2. **As a returning user**, I want to log into my dashboard, so that I can manage my applications and portfolios.

## Project Management

3. **As a user**, I want to upload project details including title, description, stack, media, and links, so that I can build a rich showcase of my work.  
4. **As a user**, I want to organize my projects by industry category, so that I can quickly filter and find relevant work for each job.

## Custom Portfolio Builder

5. **As a user**, I want to select specific projects for each job application, so that my portfolio is tailored to that role.  
6. **As a user**, I want to customize the layout, visuals, and text of my portfolio, so that it reflects my personal brand.  
7. **As a user**, I want to see a live preview of my portfolio, so that I know what recruiters will see.  
8. **As a user**, I want to generate a custom portfolio URL (e.g. `customfolio.com/kizito/stripe`), so that I can easily share my application.  
9. **As a user**, I want to download my portfolio as a PDF, so that I can attach it to applications directly.  
10. **As a user**, I want to choose from clean and bold templates, so that my portfolio looks professional and unique.  
11. **As a user**, I want to personalize fonts, colors, and logos, so that the design matches my style or target company.

## Application Tracker

12. **As a user**, I want to track the status of each job I apply to, so that I can monitor my progress (applied, interview, offer).  
13. **As a user**, I want to connect each job application to the specific portfolio I sent, so that I can evaluate what works.  
14. **As a user**, I want to receive reminders or updates, so that I don’t miss follow-ups or interviews.

## Crafting Shots (Mini Case Studies)

15. **As a user**, I want to write short, focused stories about my work ("Shots"), so that I can communicate specific skills and achievements.  
16. **As a user**, I want to attach visuals (e.g. Figma files, screenshots) to each Shot, so that I can support my claims with evidence.  
17. **As a user**, I want the system to suggest or generate Shots based on job requirements using GPT, so that I can craft relevant narratives faster.  
18. **As a user**, I want to reuse Shots across multiple portfolios, so that I don’t rewrite the same story every time.  
19. **As a user**, I want to embed Shots in different parts of my portfolio, so that my work appears tailored and engaging.
